"></span><br><span class=\"line\">遍历每个子目录，除了exploit里面还有什么？</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">每个工具分别有什么功能？原理是什么？涉及那些知识？</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">能否改进优化？能否发展、组合出新的功能？</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">以专家为线索</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">观察、分析、实践、修正</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">想提高某项技能，怎么切入？</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">观察同龄人怎么做到的，看他们是怎么做的</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">三人行必有我师。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">处理好学习、工作和生活</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">学习、工作和生活是矛盾统一的</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">三者都需要时间，一天只有24小时</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">调和矛盾的关键，提高效率</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你的学习、工作会影响能不能追求诗和远方</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">如何提高效率</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">做好预研，收集相关前人成果，避免无谓的重复劳动。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">在可行性判断阶段，能找到工具就不写代码，能用脚本语言写就不要用编译语言，把完美主义放在最终实现阶段。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">做好笔记并定期整理，遗忘会让你所有的投入白费</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">多交流，别人说一个工具的名字可能让你节约数小时</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">咖啡可以提高思维效率，而且合法。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">无论怎样提高效率，要成为专家，都需要大量的时间投入。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[{"name":"学习方法","slug":"学习方法","count":1,"path":"api/categories/学习方法.js